Pashankusa Ekadashi: It has been said that this Ekadashi is a great purifier of sins. On this day the Padmanabha form of Shri Maha Vishnu is to be specially worshipped. By accordingly worshipping the Padmanabha form of Shri Hari, one would beget all desired fruits. Fruits equal those obtained by performing great penance with extreme sense control are otained by worshipping Padmanabha on this day. One who fasts on this auspicious ekadashi would never go to hell. One begets the fruits of bathing in all holy tirthas by doing the Nama Sankirtana of Vishnu on this day. 
